      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers short, tactile throws, sending power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is paramount; this example has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and retains its original suspension geometry for unparalleled turn-in response. Every mechanical component, from the dual-mass flywheel to the cross-drilled rotors, is in peak operational state, ensuring a visceral, analog driving experience without compromise.",
